description:
&lt;p&gt;We have a vacancy for an experienced mental health nurse to join our team. The post holder will be expected to manage a caseload and act as care coordinator for a number of service users to support them in their recovery. For further information please see job description. The successful applicant would be given regular management supervision.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Trusts vision and values put are patients at the centre of everything we do, therefore you must be someone who has empathy, have an understanding and respect for the people who use are service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Any further enquiries please contact Nicky Cooper Team Coordinator on 01522 421751 or email Nicola.cooper@lpft.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that when filling out your application form to avoid delay in appointment the details of your references should be accurate, up-to date and provide work postal and email addresses to enable Employment Services to be timely in their request for your reference.&lt;/p&gt;
